title: A concept™
body:
that video of maxence skateboarding is giving me BIG elu 90’s vibes…ok…..hear me out….

so imagine that whole 90’s aesthetic with the diners, video game stores, and highchool clichés…….eliott is the popular, artistic kid at school that always carries his skateboard around and rides it whenever he can (he’s got that nice popular guy vibe going on)……..lucas is the cute nerd with a hint of spice in him that always spends his time at the library and avoids socializing at all cost (me! the socializing part not the cute part)……..eliott has no clue who lucas is, but lucas knows exactly who eliott is and aggressively denies his crush on him in fear of losing his edginess (bc what’s unique about liking the guy 99% of the student body swoons over)….lucas works at a diner and one day eliott whooshes in there on his skateboard with his big group of friends (it’s what he deserves) and they are Loud™………when he comes in lucas is all like fuck……he is forced to serve their table because literally every other waiter is busy….he takes their orders at the speed of light avoiding eliott’s eyes….when he brings in their milkshakes, he trips and spills the drinks on eliott…..he looks up and their eyes meet…..cue a flustered lucas rambling random apologies while a love struck eliott hears nothing and just focuses on the movement of his lips and wonders how it would feel like to kiss them……AFJKSKFFNFJKKSJKK

@eliottsmec @cheloueliott 👀👀👀
